          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-4459 mdt: reject RPCs sent to wrong MDT",
        "message": "LU-4459 mdt: reject RPCs sent to wrong MDT\n\nAdd a new target handler flag (HABEO_INODE) which requires that the\nobject sent in the request is an existing local object. In\nmdt_object_find_lock() return -EPROTO if the object was found to be\nremote.\n\nFOR TEST AND DISCUSSION ONLY. NOT FOR LANDING.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ieeb84f001e0ea6fd1ff55a417f13ac858ce0f8fa\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
